tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE blueprints (
    blueprint_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    blueprint_name VARCHAR(255),
    blueprint_file BYTEA,
    designer_name VARCHAR(100),
    create_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE FloorPlans (
  plan_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  plan_name VARCHAR(255),
  plan_file BYTEA,
  plan_size_in_sqft DOUBLE PRECISION,
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE analysis_results (
    analysis_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    blueprint_id UUID NOT NULL,
    analysis_type VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    analysis_result JSONB,
    analyzed_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Blueprints (
    blueprint_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    blueprint_name VARCHAR(255),
    architect_name VARCHAR(255),
    design_date DATE,
    blueprint_data BYTEA
);

CREATE TABLE Floors (
    floor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    blueprint_id INT,
    floor_number INT,
    floor_plan BYTEA,
    FOREIGN KEY (blueprint_id) REFERENCES Blueprints(blueprint_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Rooms (
    room_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    floor_id INT,
    room_name VARCHAR(255),
    room_type VARCHAR(100),
    room_area FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (floor_id) REFERENCES Floors(floor_id)
);

CREATE TABLE RoomMaterials (
    rm_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    room_id INT,
    material_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (room_id) REFERENCES Rooms(room_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (material_id) REFERENCES Materials(material_id)
);
